  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CSR-Facility. Fonden DanWatch. A strenghened watchdog who shares all its knowledge and fosters a nuanced debate</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is to strengthen Danwatch&apos;s ability to function as a watchdog on corporate responsibility. Danwatch bases its analysis on international CSR guidelines such as the UN guiding principles on Business and Human Rights, the UN Global Compact and the OECD guidelines for multinational companies.

Through investigative journalism, Danwatch aim to disclose harmful practices in international supply chains and influence Danish companies and investors to address negative impacts when doing business in developing countries. Thereby creating positive changes in the living conditions for people and impact on the environment in these countries.</narrative>
  </description>
